Package com.cafean.client.ui.swing.accordion

Enum NodeState

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<NodeState>
      • com.cafean.client.ui.swing.accordion.NodeState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<NodeState>
    public enum NodeState
extends java.lang.Enum<NodeState>
    NodeState contains the colors used to paint NodeButtons given a given the button's state as contracted/expanded, highlighted, and pressed. Additionally, separate states are provided for the various Classifications.

      • getNodeState

        public static NodeState getNodeState​(boolean expanded,
                                     boolean pressed,
                                     boolean highlighted,
                                     Classification classification)
        Returns the NodeState appropriate for the given parameters.
        Parameters:
        expanded - the expanded status of the requested state
        pressed - the pressed status of the requested state (takes precedence over highlighted)
        highlighted - the highlighted status of the requested state
        classification - the classification type of the requested state
        Returns:
        a NodeState matching the requested parameters.
